Class SSListenerStringVal

  • java.lang.Object

    public class SSListenerStringVal
extends SSBaseListener
implements SSListener
    StringVal are string values (possibly null). They are stored internally as valid fragments of java code, e.g., Strings are quoted.
    Author:
    xavier
